{"tid":1663311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大埔連儂隧道男街坊派傳單遇襲 遭劏肚腸溢出重創","createTime":"2019-10-19T10:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T11:30:46.000Z","uid":68738,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4b28d3d001603d22dd088ca55e653673476e42","tid":1663311,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191019/large/1571481023_13b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191019%2Flarge%2F1571481023_13b0.jpg&h=237c9b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大埔發生斬人案，下午5時許，有街坊於大埔連儂隧道派傳單期間，一名黑衫男子將牆上的memo紙撕下，其間與街坊爭執，黑衫男突然取出利刀襲擊一名男街坊的頸部，傷者倒地後，狂徒再上前向其腹部刺一刀，腸臟外露，狂徒逞兇後登上的士離去。警方其後接報到場，將傷者送往沙田威爾斯醫院搶救。"},{"pid":"a9c71089c64a6b8f0c294e2d919212311c8118b9","tid":1663311,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:40:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191019/60172810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191019%2F60172810&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=4af045ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191019%2F60172810&h=0f159c4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191019/60172810</a>"},{"pid":"85bc1908368ca51dfb9c15343bd102f09656bfe9","tid":1663311,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:41:19.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb74c333d47a4977eb01739fd06a5cf9fb3b17b","tid":1663311,"uid":103759,"like":1,"disl